data.description:
Who is in the market for a great home in NW OKC? This property located in a cozy neighborhood with pond, and will not disappoint. This wonderful home puts you in a convenient spot near turnpike and major highways, dining, entertainment, shopping, etc. This home has new carpet, fresh paint, has been refreshed, and is ready for you to make it your own. The semi open living area is great size with raised ceilings, fireplace, and built in bookshelves. There are also double french doors with built in blinds that lead you out to your covered patio and backyard. Your kitchen and dining area is open to the living room. The kitchen has a good amount of storage and counter space. As you walk through the hallway there are two bedrooms that are well sized, and the front bedroom has a ton of natural light from multiple windows. The master bedroom is at the end of the hall and has raised ceilings as well as being a large room. The master bathroom is open, with a stand up shower, separate garden tub, dual vanity, and a large walk-in closet. 

This home gives so much potential to personalize, make it your own, and is located in a great area of the metro.
